We are looking for a skilled and experienced Senior AI Engineer specializing in LLM to join our dynamic team. As a key member, you will drive the development and deployment of advanced AI/ML models with a strong focus on security applications.




Description:

 * Build, deploy, and optimize AI models, ensuring high performance and accuracy, focusing on security applications, particularly Embedding Models and Liveness Detection Methods;
 * Contribute to the development of Large Language Models (LLM), Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG), and chatbot applications to enhance system interactions;
 * Collaborate closely with other teams to ensure AI solutions align with project requirements and security standards;
 * Ensure projects are finished on time, and meet quality standards;
 * Coordinate with cross-functional teams to integrate solutions into the broader system architecture;
 * Mentor and support team members in their professional development.




Requirement:

Technical Skills:

